real Mr. Finger.

00:49.211 --> 00:50.377
Oh, my God, he was available?

00:50.379 --> 00:51.913
Luckily he hadn't worked
in 22 years.

00:51.915 --> 00:53.047
I-I used to love
Mr. Finger.

00:53.049 --> 00:54.516
I dressed up as him
for Halloween.

00:54.518 --> 00:55.952
Uh, did you wear the
glove year-round?

00:55.954 --> 00:57.152
Did people mistake you
for Michael Jackson?

00:57.154 --> 00:58.387
Did you know, in
your heart of hearts,

00:58.389 --> 00:59.621
