01:20.805 --> 01:22.038
Do you ever listen to yourself?

01:22.040 --> 01:23.005
Mr. Hastings,
I'm Sydney.

01:23.007 --> 01:24.873
We spoke on the phone. Oh,

01:24.875 --> 01:29.176
