how D-level they are

04:38.926 --> 04:40.959
You should be ashamed
of yourself.

04:40.961 --> 04:42.527
You can apologize
in the morning.

04:42.529 --> 04:45.763
Oh, God, am I hungry.

04:45.765 --> 04:47.231
I had such a wonderful night.

04:47.233 --> 04:49.699
Yeah. And the best part is, it
all took place in the afternoon.

04:49.701 --> 04:51.667
The irony is,
in my sunset years

04:51.669 --> 04:52.967
I have yet to see one.

04:54.570 --> 04:57.170
I was worried you'd be bored by an
old man like me. Are you kidding?

04:57.172 --> 04:59.339
When was the last time
I went on a date with a man

04:59.341 --> 05:01.107
that shared my love
of Murder, She Wrote?

05:01.109 --> 05:03.076
Yeah. Okay, let
me get you a cab.

05:03.078 --> 05:04.679
You have a big day
ahead of you tomorrow.

05:08.752 --> 05:10.585
My dear,

05:10.587 --> 05:13.154
you've worn me out.

05:13.156 --> 05:15.924
Would you please close the door

05:15.926 --> 05:18.093
after me?

05:18.095 --> 05:21.163
Good-bye, my darling,
until next time.

