of interest.

06:10.482 --> 06:11.915
We can't have two
car dealerships.

06:13.117 --> 06:15.118
Oh.

06:15.120 --> 06:17.220
Pete Hadary was
our very first account.

06:17.222 --> 06:18.788
But if Ford finds out...

06:18.790 --> 06:21.190
They'd fire us and we'd lose
our credibility.

06:21.192 --> 06:23.393
Simon, you know
how I feel about you.

06:23.395 --> 06:24.795
I'd carry your hair in a locket

06:24.797 --> 06:27.163
- if necklaces weren't weird on guys.
- Mmhmm.

06:27.165 --> 06:29.366
But do you think that this
is really worth the risk?

06:29.368 --> 06:32.068
Son, we have to have
some accounts

06:32.070 --> 06:33.436
where it's not just
about the money.

06:33.438 --> 06:36.005
The Stan Woods let
you sleep at night.

06:36.007 --> 06:37.207
I find an orgasm helps.

06:37.209 --> 06:38.808
I used to throw, like,
a fistful of downers

06:38.810 --> 06:40.943
into a blender
with cough syrup and warm milk.

06:40.945 --> 06:42.444
I called it Milk of Amnesia,

06:42.446 --> 06:43.945
but then sobriety
ruined all that.

06:43.947 --> 06:46.514
Now I need nonsense
like loyalty and ethics

06:46.516 --> 06:48.716
to get through the night.

06:50.452 --> 06:53.688
It was like a lizard flicking
its tongue in my mouth...

06:53.690 --> 06:56.723
or its tail...
whatever is grosser.

06:56.725 --> 06:58.758
Huh, so you
and Mr. Finger.

06:58.760 --> 07:00.427
Yeah, I can totally see that.

07:00.429 --> 07:01.628
That's your takeaway
from my story?

07:01.630 --> 07:04.031
An old man French-kissed me.

07:04.033 --> 07:06.032
I skew older sometimes, too.

07:06.034 --> 07:07.200
It takes a different skill set

07:07.202 --> 07:08.901
but can be
well worth the effort.

07:08.903 --> 07:12.905
Turns out stories of the old
country... really tutu me on.

07:12.907 --> 07:14.774
Why do I confide in you people?

07:14.776 --> 07:16.242
Just to blame the victim
for a minute here,

07:16.244 --> 07:17.978
are you sure
this isn't your fault?

07:17.980 --> 07:19.046
He assaulted me.

07:19.048 --> 07:19.980
You kind of led him on.

07:19.982 --> 07:21.748
Well, how?
How?

07:21.750 --> 07:23.016
You were all over him.

07:23.018 --> 07:25.119
"Well, aren't you
charming and handsome?

07:25.121 --> 07:27.521
How are you single?"

07:27.523 --> 07:29.590
