07:29.592 --> 07:30.858
Hmm, kind of was.

07:30.860 --> 07:34.528
Okay, maybe I said one thing.

07:34.530 --> 07:35.629
"I'll take Glenn out.

07:35.631 --> 07:38.599
That way I get him
all to myself."

07:38.601 --> 07:40.234
