07:40.236 --> 07:41.202
"It's a date.

07:41.204 --> 07:43.103
How do you like your eggs?"

07:43.105 --> 07:45.840
Well, that last
part was implied.

07:45.842 --> 07:47.308
That was old man flirting.

07:47.310 --> 07:48.743
I didn't think it counted.

07:48.745 --> 07:50.245
He's not dead; of course
he's going to succumb

07:50.247 --> 07:52.180
to a pretty girl
that's coming on to him.

07:52.182 --> 07:53.849
Oh, my God, you guys are right.

07:53.851 --> 07:56.618
You're being mean about it,
but you're right.

07:56.620 --> 07:58.153
I feel so bad.

07:58.155 --> 07:59.454
Well, you should.

07:59.456 --> 08:00.756
He's a man
with a heart and a soul,

08:00.758 --> 08:03.291
