08:17.975 --> 08:20.475
Yeah, I love you, too, honey.

08:20.477 --> 08:22.077
Yeah, yeah, I said it, o-o-okay.

08:22.079 --> 08:23.145
Simon!

08:23.147 --> 08:24.479
You bellowed? This
may be a surprise,

08:24.481 --> 08:26.648
but I called the contact number

08:26.650 --> 08:28.383
for Stan Wood,
and it went straight

08:28.385 --> 08:30.018
