08:30.020 --> 08:31.853
Oh, you are
an amazing storyteller.

08:31.855 --> 08:33.154
How you spin a yarn.

08:33.155 --> 08:34.722
Okay, don't play that
game with me, tiny man.

08:34.724 --> 08:36.657
I'm starving,
I'll eat your head.

08:36.659 --> 08:37.991
Okay.

08:37.994 --> 08:39.126
Lauren, will you please find

08:39.129 --> 08:40.695
the correct number
for Stan Wood?

08:40.697 --> 08:42.464
Okay, it might take me a while.

08:42.466 --> 08:43.565
I'll wait... uh,
you know what?

08:43.567 --> 08:44.699
Better yet, why
don't you get him

08:44.701 --> 08:46.468
on the line for me right now?

08:46.470 --> 08:48.936
Lauren, let me help you
with that.

08:50.172 --> 08:52.306
Oh, hey, Gordon,
that's a great shirt.

08:52.308 --> 08:53.708
Who is that?
I don't know.

08:53.710 --> 08:55.109
Do you mind if I grab a ladder
and check the tag? Shirt.

08:56.279 --> 08:57.912
I just want to see the tag.
All right, relax.

08:57.914 --> 09:01.216
Ralph Lauren, wow, nice,
nice, worth the climb.

