09:46.398 --> 09:48.398
Oh, that is a great question.

09:48.400 --> 09:50.333
You know, it's one
for the ages.

09:50.335 --> 09:52.102
I remember, is a beautiful city

09:52.104 --> 09:53.670
with many city streets
and buildings,

09:53.672 --> 09:54.871
lots of building.

09:54.873 --> 09:56.273
It's in the middle of Poland.

09:56.275 --> 09:58.375
You know, I think
its name is...

09:58.377 --> 09:59.276
Warsaw.

09:59.278 --> 10:00.511
Ah, Warsaw.

10:00.513 --> 10:02.379
Is this the road
we're gonna go down, Simon?

10:02.381 --> 10:04.214
